      • addItemElements

        public void addItemElements(org.jsoup.select.Elements elems)
        Fills itemList from an Elements object by iterating through the list of Elements and creating a new Item object for each. Items are either ProductItem or DealItem; type defaults to ProductItem if a type cannot be found.
        Parameters:
        elems - the list of Elements to be converted to items and added to itemsList
